Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想今天下的雨不會停吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得真大  這樣做工作也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天大家都休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎  外面的世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會因下雨或下雪而休息的公司和學校幾乎沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說辛苦還是勤奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不偶爾無所事事　好好悠閒地休息的話會累得喘不過氣來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我還是喜歡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像喜歡工作的小鈴的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:05.01,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HB82C45}雨也是…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想至少在下雨有空的時候試著做下菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是味噌湯  湯幾乎沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點奇怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很喜歡這味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後也偶爾做做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是奇怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣悠閒地吃早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨嗎  真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:20.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應用著「貓洗臉就會下雨」的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我所發明的天氣預報試做第二號失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:26.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用飛木屐占卜天氣的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的試作第一號也是準確率只有二成以下的大失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能預測天氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能給農作業或別的什麼提供很多幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說「青蛙感覺快要下雨時會呱呱kerokero叫」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去調查青蛙的生態（聲帶）吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是叫「學校泳裝」 是外面世界水中用的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中用?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要穿著這個就算進多少水也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去實驗學校泳裝的性能和調查青蛙  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐  請小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校泳裝絕佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…靜…不…下…來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在日本時  不是學習就是和爺爺練習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是比普通人都要忙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣的我悠閒地過一整天是不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句話來說是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就來玩翻花繩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻花繩?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒玩過  那個  大概不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丟布包或彈玻璃球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下將棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  將棋不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小鈴會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小看我  我很擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不錯的將棋板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過飛車是紙做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為壞了而代替一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓行人輸慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到的話就試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭  剪刀  布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我先手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  論實力我後手正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不服輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小鈴在家裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自從行人來下雨休息是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人來那天之前是大暴風雨非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許多東西被吹飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像大小屋頂還有綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出入島和暴風雨有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前婆婆們也說漂流到這裡是有大暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨的日子那些大漩渦變弱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到小鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小鈴偶爾會流露出寂寞的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦  下雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因為下雨而待著不動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥  做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出的題目的櫃子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然花了點時間  做的不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外觀不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個其實是拉門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為做抽屜很難啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就繼續做學徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就是我就二十連勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要來一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小鈴將棋還真強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的下雨天經常會陪我下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨  討厭雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為仙貝受潮了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這憤怒該如何平息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會發洩在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的珍藏  要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我特製的激辣丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…給我水…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太得意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為可以逃得掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  贏了  贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪雪真強…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不讓你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法  一直都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓…住…了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木莓？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（薔薇科懸鉤子植物的總稱）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不錯的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音也要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜  麻知姐  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的  很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  千影姐不在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來今天沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「學校泳衣」實驗失敗中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  千影姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來做午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴今天會偶爾覺得寂寞是回憶起媽媽的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雨天幾乎一直都在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有許多和媽媽一起玩的回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過媽媽不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴雨天一直都孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個家裡  孤獨一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著雨聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感覺沒有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  小鈴  偷跑?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁誰都不在居然襲擊行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在這樣的雨天都怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺大家偶然閒的湊在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小鈴姐  這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好香  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝  是小凜做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我是木匠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  我帶這個過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  綾音  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  這個  收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛  謝謝  千影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  正好在準備午飯  得做許多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待小鈴姐的午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前是掛麵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不硬不軟汁也是…忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:41.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛麵也好  但烏龍麵也不錯  蕎麥麵和飯團也不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是偶然  其實是為了小鈴而聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  大姐頭是為了吃而來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:46.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:48.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真敢說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴就算是雨天也不是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:55.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別分心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如此溫柔的朋友守護著她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  大家是好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴吃午飯之前能借一下浴室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的  要感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感…感覺有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼行人大人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許真有一天我會失血過多而死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  小鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下小了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會像今天一樣大家都會來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著什麼偶然的笨拙的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴果然也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在大家回去後還是有點寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和行人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有月亮大人在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:53.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨降りお月さん雲の蔭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:53.24,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雨中的月亮 藏在雲朵中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:53.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「雨降りお月さん」野口雨情作詞 中山晉平作曲／大正14年）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:19:01.00,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お嫁にゆくときゃ　誰とゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:19:01.00,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}如果要嫁出去要嫁給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是以前外面世界的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽常常唱給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想繼續聽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:20.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人で傘（からかさ）　さしてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:20.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}獨自撐著紙傘 走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:28.22,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘（からかさ）ないときゃ　誰とゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:28.22,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是沒有了紙傘 又會和誰在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:36.12,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャラシャラ　シャンシャン　鈴つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:36.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}風鈴 沙沙地 叮鈴叮鈴地響著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:44.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お馬に揺られて濡れて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:44.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}馬兒搖搖晃晃地 濕漉漉地走著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:20:01.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いそがにゃお馬よ　夜が明けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:20:01.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}快點走啊馬兒 馬上要天明了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:09.77,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手綱（たづな）の下から　チョイと見たりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:09.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}順著韁繩 悄悄地看了看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:17.68,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お袖（そで）でお顔を　かくしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:17.68,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我用袖擺遮掩面容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:25.61,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お袖はぬれても　乾（ほ）しゃかわく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:25.61,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就算袖擺濕了 曬乾就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:33.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨降りお月さん　雲の蔭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:33.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雨中的月亮 藏在雲朵中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:41.98,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お馬にゆられて　ぬれてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:41.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}馬兒搖搖晃晃地 濕漉漉地走著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會和出色的女婿邂逅的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  會穿著媽媽穿過的新娘服成為可愛的新娘的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴的媽媽這樣說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很會漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴做新娘樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  不可能沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人究竟在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆大福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}怎麼可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:30.07,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「感冒了…去取冰」
